buildArgs, while I'm curious if there's a module system at play within the runtime of an image. There’s definitely a lot to unpack here!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_7EgCwrsJjt9MCW1gT0s1MFu9|fc_03dc36b585fb3d800169f1be078c2481958895ab910927cdd5", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "git status --short --untracked-files=all && git log --oneline -1", "timeout": 10}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 675, "output": 1860, "cacheRead": 46080, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48615, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777450477691, "responseId": "resp_03dc36b585fb3d800169f1bdee406c819586b9f78e79bfc52a"}}
